text: Ra lutako kaumaka manisaharu unitarpha daudera a'e. Ra yiniharu aghi dekhinai aslilakarma garne garthe. Lutale bhaneh ‘‘ki he mero kaumaka manisaharu yi mero choriharu hun jo timra nimti pavitra chin, tasartha allahasita dara ra mera pahunaharuko barema mala'i apamanita nagara. Ke timiharumadhye kohi pani bhalo manche chaina
